<div class="related_info">
  






  

  <h2>
    <span>内容简介</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>



<div class="indent" id="link-report">
    
      <div class="">
        <style type="text/css" media="screen">
.intro p{text-indent:2em;word-break:normal;}
</style>
<div class="intro">
    <p>（全1冊）以超人氣之姿出道，僅以一年時光便晉身為超級巨星的搖滾樂團「ENDORPHINES」，然而歌迷的連續自殺行為與主唱．戒音周圍的種種怪事不斷發生…！讀者引頸期盼的震撼懸疑之作！除了「戒音」外，另收錄3篇初期作品。</p></div>

      </div>
    

</div>

  
      

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://img9.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/other/online-partner.36905.css">


  




<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://img1.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/subject/authors_section.6022b.css">

<h2>
    
  

  <h2>
    <span>戒音的创作者</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


</h2>
<div class="indent">
    <p></p>
    <div id="authors" class="authors">
    <ul class="authors-list from-subject __oneline">
            
            <li class="author">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/139093/" title="由贵香织里">
                    <img src="https://img9.doubanio.com/img/author/raw/public/1492147164.16.jpg" alt="由贵香织里" class="avatar">
                </a>
                <div class="info">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/139093/" title="由贵香织里" class="name">由贵香织里</a>
                    <span class="role">作者</span>
                </div>
            </li>
             
            
            <li class="author">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/4526586/" title="由貴香織里">
                    <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/pics/author-default-medium.png" alt="由貴香織里" class="avatar">
                </a>
                <div class="info">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/4526586/" title="由貴香織里" class="name">由貴香織里</a>
                    <span class="role">作者</span>
